    Developer website

    Description

    RealHomes – Estate Sale and Rental WordPress Theme – Reliable, Customizable and Versatile real estate WordPress theme. Number #1 best seller real estate theme on Themeforest.

    Manage & Modify The RealHomes Search Forms Visually with Drag-&-Drop Contols. Field Builder to Add New Fields

    • Highly Customizable and Feature Rick Real Estate Search Forms
    • Multiple Search Form Layouts and Multiple Layouts for Search Results page are provided and more will be added in future updates.
    • Customize What Fields to Display in the Top Row of a Search Form and the order in which they appear.
    • Extend Location Field to Up to 4 fields. To offer selection choices like Country > State > City > District.
    • Dynamic Locations Loading can be enabled when dealing with hundreds or thousands of locations.
    • Exlude a Group of Properties from search if needed.
    • Order/Sort Search Fields in any way and Show/Hide any Search Field.
    • Allow Multi-Select Functionality for certain fields.
    • Alphabetic Sorting of values and Empty Value Hiding can be enabled where applicable.
    • Field Values can be Added/Modified as per requirement.
    • Separate Prices fields for For-Sale & For-Rent searches.
    • Measurement Unit, Currency Symbol and Price Format can be replaced/customized as per requirement.
    • Highly Customizable Search Widget for Elementor is also provided.
    • Additional/New Fields can be added to search form.
    • Various other Features and Flexibilities…

    Elementor Page Builder – Lost of Flexibility Provided Throug Elementor Widgets. 35 RealHomes Based Elementor Widgets Inroduced

    • Advanced Real Estate Search Widget
    • 5 Properties Widgets
    • 2 Agents Widgets
    • 2 Blog Posts Widgets
    • 4 Testimonials Widgets
    • Modal Login Widget
    • Google Maps Widget
    • Agent Profile Widget
    • Locations/Cities Widget
    • 4 Featured Properties Widgets
    • 2 Features Widgets
    • Partners Widget
    • Section Title Widget
    • 3 Call to Action Widgets
    • Slogan Widget
    • OpenStreetMaps Widget
    • Agent Contact Form Widget
    • Various other widgets

    Vacation Rentals – Functionality is introduced in RealHomes 3.12. Now you can build a Property Booking website using RealHomes Nulled.

    • Booking Widget is provided for property detail page. Booking requests are added to database and emailed to admin. Customer gets email updates when booking status gets changed by admin.
    • Availability Calendar is also provided for property page that displays available dates for booking based on confirmed bookings for current property.
    • Vacation Rentals Search Form is provided to search available properties based on given dates and number of guests.
    • Vacation Rentals Specific Modules are provided for property detail page. To display various details about property rules, features and surroundings.

    User/Member’s Dashboard

    • A user can easily submit new properties and manage (edit or remove) his existing properties from newly provided dashboard.
    • User can also manage his Membership/Subscription Package based on how much properties he needs to publish.
    • User can keep his contact info, social media URLs and profile information up-to-date.
    • A user can view and manage his favorite properties.

    More features are coming …
